attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Realty Of The Treasure Coast
Keller Williams Realty Of The Treasure Coast

data.description: The perfect opportunity for low maintenance living in Martin County!  All Ages and pet-friendly townhouse/villa in the sought-after Heritage Ridge "Yorktown" neighborhood.  New Roof and AC in 2022!  This two bedroom, two bath, one car garage unit is perfectly located on a corner lot - adding to the sense of privacy, as well as natural light at all times.  This is the former sales model, and its great bones are ready for your personal touches.  Inside, find soaring ceilings and a split floor plan.  Kitchen is efficient in design and opens up to the living areas.  Master suite is ample, and guests will feel more than welcome in the guest room and bath.  One car garage adds to the utility.   Outside, enjoy the screened covered lanai, giving a place for relaxation.  Appropriately priced for the potential, this configuration will allow for easy personal touches.  The Heritage Ridge community also offers community pool/tennis/pickleball for a nominal additional fee of $495!
